00:29:35,250 --> 00:29:36,746
I think I'll be here late.

578
00:29:37,002 --> 00:29:38,189
What about you?

579
00:29:39,879 --> 00:29:41,178
I'll probably be at university

580
00:29:41,203 --> 00:29:42,483
until late, too.

581
00:29:44,050 --> 00:29:45,235
Then...

582
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:46,332
Do you want to grab

583
00:29:46,357 --> 00:29:47,389
