584
00:30:16,374 --> 00:30:17,534
Kim Suhyeon?

585
00:30:27,177 --> 00:30:28,595
It was all a misunderstanding.

586
00:30:30,305 --> 00:30:32,101
Thinking I could reach for him.

587
00:30:32,689 --> 00:30:34,149
A foolish delusion.

588
00:30:38,772 --> 00:30:39,920
Yeah.

589
00:30:40,315 --> 00:30:41,518
This is how it should be.

590
00:30:42,317 --> 00:30:43,337
Love is for people

591
00:30:43,357 --> 00:30:44,637
